---
title: Chermoula Chicken, Chickpea & Pumpkin Buddha Bowl with Zingy Radish Slaw & Garlic Dip
description: This nourishing bowl will leave you feeling satisfied and energised in equal measure. Between crunchy cabbage, roasted pumpkin and tasty chickpeas, every bite is a delight. Our favourite flourish is the rich garlic dip dolloped on top.

*We’ve replaced the coriander in this recipe with mint due to local ingredient availability. It may be a little different to what’s pictured, but just as delicious!*

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/664586282537d3c1a9bdd4ba-e206cae0.jpeg
